ation\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously I would not have said yes if I did not think my body and mind were up to it, because there is a huge amount of work that goes into getting there.\\\"\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge amount\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Storey's family are very much along from the ride.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Storey's family\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the ride\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Husband Barney, a triple Paralympic champion himself as a sighted pilot, co-manages their eponymous Storey Racing trade team and daughter Louisa has spent plenty of time with them at stage races.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barney_Stinson\", \"score\": 0.9999999995907274, \"rank\": 2.1185779229987716e-10, \"text\": \"Barney\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barney_Stinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barney_Stinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a triple Paralympic champion\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"a sighted pilot\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"their eponymous Storey Racing trade team\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"daughter Louisa\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"stage races\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the inspiration that children get from being around elite sport is really difficult to explain,\\\" said Storey, one of over 1,000 elite athletes on UK Sport's National Lottery-funded World Class Programme, allowing her to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering medical support.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the inspiration\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sport\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"Storey\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My kids are very aware of race day preparation!\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My kids\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"race day preparation\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They almost have this secret superpower because it's so rare you get to experience something like that up close.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this secret superpower\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a unique opportunity for them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a unique opportunity\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley wasinspired to come out of retirementby his son, Robbie, and Storey knows exactly how the Team GB legend feels.\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2123, \"end\": 2132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.419369837122283e-32, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 2182, \"end\": 2188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"score\": 0.9999986577772602, \"rank\": 1.3421922150245183e-06, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Donnachaidh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"retirementby\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2172}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"Storey\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"the Team GB legend\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I read what Tom had said, I could completely get what he was saying,\\\" said Storey.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"Storey\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's in the same place as me - if the body is willing, we will be there.\\\"\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same place\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Life is about a lot more than the bike for Storey these days, with her role as Active Travel Commissioner for Greater Manchester taking up a great deal of time.\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Life\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2449}, {\"ngram\": \"Storey\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"her role\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"Active Travel Commissioner\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"Greater Manchester\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"a great deal\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It means that her approach to training, recovery and everything in between has evolved significantly.\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her approach\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As an older athlete, working and working out the next step in my life is part of the bigger picture,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an older athlete\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"the next step\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"the bigger picture\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It means I definitely train differently.\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still have the same intense training camps I have always had and they work incredibly well for me - I have got a really good base that I go to regularly where the children are very well looked after.\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same intense training camps\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"a really good base\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"the children\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some things have changed and some things have stayed the same but I am very mindful that your body changes with age as well.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some things\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"some things\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"your body\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am working closely with people who are going to help me adapt things as necessary over the next few months.\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3194}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few months\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am pushing the boundaries and there are not many athletes who are competing over the age of 45 and trying to get back to the top of the podium.\", \"from\": 3273, \"to\": 3419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boundaries\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3301}, {\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3364}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3404}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am kind of pushing on that feeling again, a little bit like I did when I came back from having children in the first place.\\\"\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3456}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"the first place\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Getting that transition right feels crucial to the next stage of Storey's remarkable career, on and off the bike.\", \"f